profile_positions.description:
Job Mission:
Participation in FMO Program (Future Mode of Operations) for Customer Support (approx 3500 Engineers World Wide) in a SAP Greenfield approach. Facilitate and drive together with a team the (re-)design, build and implementation of the ASML’s End-to-End processes and supporting IT infrastructure (SAP).

Job Description:
End-to-End processes definition and business architecture based on standard solutions and best practices;
Select best practices most suitable to ASML’s business characteristics and needs;
Analyze impact of new concepts for existing ways of working and determine implementation strategies; Be the linking factor between the IT-system (SAP) and business processes; Gather best practices and think out the impact of new concepts for current way of working; Re-engineer business processes, based on standard solutions and best practices; 
Facilitate business change aspects like decision making, gather requirements and feedback;
Set up and facilitate execution of implementation and roll out plans including testing, key user and end user training, shop floor introduction, Test, train and do change management during implementation phase to to ensure a smooth introduction and transition.
